values: yea as from the comments i got from ppl saying i suck at drums i do iv never had a drum lesson in my life so i cant play and plus 3 days of practice doesnt help either and also id like to see you organize a show better then me so if you can do it and prove it to me be my guest anyways i think it went well and im glad i played cuz i did it for fun not to try to win anything cuz being a musician is about havign fun with wut your doing

Holy shit OZZFEST was great went with my friend keith, sarah, yours truly, my gf meaghan, keiths bro, his dad, and his dads friend It was fucking great all the bands kicked ass got autographs from Slipknot (sorry to those, they only allowed 1 sig of the 3 members that were there for the signing) and i also got sigs from the 3 members of Dimmu Borgir that were at the signing. The main stage was great but the great OZZY had bronchitus and couldnt sing so the singer from Judas Priest sang so we left. Dimmu's performance was awsome but i thought there would be more of a show. (Cradles performance of last years was best iv ever seen so far) wen the pics get in ill be sure to show you all got sum great pics of the bands. As usual had a fuckign great time. laters.
